title: MotoGP 2016 Round 14 Aragon 720p 50fps Enhanced Audio
description:
This video is RACE ONLY, but with an additional audio track I call "Enhanced". Enhanced means the bikes and ambient sounds have been boosted so you can actually hear them as well as the commentary. The broadcasters obviously feel that it's all about the commentators and it's been getting worse every year. I played a video with the standard audio track for someone and they asked me what was wrong with the sound since they couldn't hear the motorcycles. 

My Internet upload speed is pretty slow, so it takes a while to seed files of this size.

Enjoy!
